Then Ten dropped birthday. It was good for me. 
But DANGEROUS?! Is Dangerous. That song is literally so good. I'm glad for the performance video, because I wanted to see it.
Ten now places in my top Ten. This entire album was good and too short.

author: @aejyl1080
text:
1. Wow... just wow!  Can't wait to hear both songs in full, Dangerous in particular, that choreo is 🔥🔥🔥 and the editing is so good.
2. Funny how phone booths still pop up as props in MVs; there was one in Broken Melodies, OOO also had one in their 'Be series', and now Ten. I like the aesthetics though, looks very eerie 👻
Fun fact, if you manage to find a phone booth that's still in use, and you dial your birthdate, your dark doppelgänger gets summoned 😆👌
I can't wait for the album to drop, literally counting the days. I hope Ten gets all the success and recognition he deserves 💚 🌹🍀💯

author: @aligensa
text: I love Ten, and I was so excited that he would do a solo release, but so far I'm deeply disappointed, even though his performance is great. The teaser photos looked avantgarde and artistic, but the videos and music are bland and lack originality. The style of this looks too much like Jungkook's "Standing Next To You", and the Matrix is overused, eg also in Minho's "Heartbreak". He deserves much better! I'm also disappointed that he sings in English, although I admit since he is Thai and speaks English well it at least makes more sense to choose English rather than Korean or Thai, because the audience wouldn't be used to that.

text: Ten, the charismatic and versatile member of NCT, takes the stage with an agile and dynamic presence that immediately captivates the audience. His hypnotic and mesmerizing performances showcase a fearless and daring approach to dance, leaving spectators in awe of his skillful and innovative moves. Ten's sleek and stylish demeanor, combined with a contemporary and progressive fashion sense, makes him a trendsetting icon. With a magnetic and electrifying aura, he exudes confidence and charm, embodying a unique and unconventional spirit. Ten's playful and spirited energy, along with his suave and cool demeanor, creates an unforgettable and impactful experience for fans. His imaginative and artistic expressions, paired with a polished and sophisticated stage presence, contribute to his iconic status as a masterful and phenomenal performer. In every performance, Ten delivers a dazzling and sizzling show that is both infectious and vivid, solidifying his place as a true sensation in the worl
